            <h3>📊 Detailed Tracking</h3>
            <p>Track specifications, modifications, maintenance history, and current market value.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>🌐 Share & Connect</h3>
            <p>Share your garage publicly, compare bikes with others, and discover new models.</p>
